# AuditFlow Roadmap 

Our mission is to automate the "boring stuff" in compliance so engineers can focus on building.

###  Q1 2026: The Foundation
- [ ] Core CLI tool for local scanning.
- [ ] Support for **Terraform** and **CloudFormation** keyword checks.
- [ ] Initial "FedRAMP-Style" report template.

###  Q2 2026: Automation & Integration
- [ ] **GitHub Actions** integration for automated report generation.
- [ ] Support for **SOC2 Type 1** mapping.
- [ ] Interactive architecture diagrams via Mermaid.js.

###  Q3 2026: Enterprise Scaling
- [ ] Support for **Kubernetes** manifest scanning.
- [ ] **ISO 27001** and **HIPAA** compliance templates.
- [ ] Multi-cloud support (AWS, Azure, GCP).
